<br>
He straightened one of the sleeves on his tunic and walked over to Eris herself, giving his step-mother a &quot;Let me try...&quot; look. His warm golden aura glew a bit lighter, he loved the thrill of a challenge such as this one.<br>
<br>
He looked down at Eris, as he was standing, and took one last sip of his wine.<br>
<br>
