<br>
&quot;Now that was party...&quot; he thought to himself.<br>
<br>
Suddenly he felt a pair of slender milky white arms embrace him, bringing him back to reality. <br>
<br>
&quot;Oh its just Persephone...no need to freak out.&quot; he sighed in releif.<br>
He hugged her and kissed her on the cheek.<br>
<br>
He smiled as she spoke of his travels and what not.<br>
<br>
&quot;Yes, it would be nice of us to travel together, we seem to share a common interest in the world outside of Greece.&quot;<br>
<br>
Smiling and nodding to Persephone and Eris, he waltzed his way across the room to his sister Athena and Nike.<br>
<br>
He took a sip of his wine and looked around. He looked to the girls and made a face like:<br>
&quot;Oh my Zeus, can somebody just get the ball rolling.&quot; and rolled his eyes. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#6A74B4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=hypnos>Hypnos </A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_bluespot.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Silver Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 201<br> <font color=#FFFF00>(10/27/01 4:19 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm32.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2.topic&index=73>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=C:\WINDOWS\Desktop\Stuff\hypnos.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Promise of Entertainment</span><hr size=1> (Apollo, look at my last post.) <p>~*~*~*~*~Thè göd öƒ §|èèp~*~*~*~*~        </p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#6A74B4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uthegreatapollo.showPublicProfile?language=EN>The Great Apollo</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Bronze Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 108<br> <font color=#FFFF00>(10/27/01 5:39 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm32.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2.topic&index=74>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Apologies</span><hr size=1> Apollo turned around to see his friend and relative Hypos. Apollo nodded and smiled as Hypnos apologized to him.<br>
