<br>
'Sure I am, though everyone seems so lethargic and to keep to themselves.'<br>
<br>
::He looks over to a gathering of many river gods a few yards away.::<br>
<br>
'I guess I should find some people to do something with. I'm thinking about going over there with those River dieties, they seem to be having a ball.'<br>
<br>
::The river dieties talk loudly to one another and laugh. They drink to one another and to the married couple and some are even wrestling one another in trails of strength. One of the wrestlers is slammed into the ground and sinks deeply into it. He gets back up and after he wipes himself clean of the grains of dirt resumes his wrestling match with entusiasm. <br>
<br>
Poseidon looks back down at Eris and in a quick movement takes hold of her shoulders, pulls her to him and kisses her on the lips. He than presses her away gently and gathers his composure.::<br>
<br>
'Let the party begin then. I'll be over there with the other water dieties. Come if you want, unless you have other plans.'<br>
<br>
::He walks by her and turns back to her. He blows her a kiss and walks up to the other gods.:: <p>Poseidon~Lord of the Deep Blue Sea~Patron Of Horses And Sailors~</p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uposeidonkofc.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Poseidonkofc</A> at: 10/30/01 12:47:41 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#6A74B4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uqueenhera.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Queen Hera</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Bronze Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 161<br> <font color=#FFFF00>(10/30/01 5:39 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm32.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2.topic&index=78>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Apologies</span><hr size=1> Hera had stood there watching the scene for a bit.   She knew her daughter was calculating something, but was unsure what it was.  And nor did she fear it, whatever was being planned was not going to do anything but cause upheaval.  That was what Eris was all about.  And hafl the time, Hera didn't mind being apart of it.  <br>
<br>
Her cold eyes scanned and watched the other gods.  She knew Artemis was standing at her side.  They two of them having much in common for standing up for womenkind.  Her site caught Poseidon making a fool of himself with Eris and rolled her eyes.  Surely, he wasn't that stupid to know Eris was only probably using him.  And well, so was he probably using her.  She was further surprised to see him walk over to be with some of the minor river dieties.  For they were her's, much to the unliking of the King of the Oceans.  Hera shrugged it off and looked to the couple, who were now ignoring all the Olympian discord.  They were mingling with their friends now and seeming to be content to ignore troubles. <p>~~<<<<<<{{{{@</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#6A74B4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/bamazonsunite.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=hypnos>Hypnos </A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_bluespot.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Silver Warrior</span><br>  Posts: 203<br> <font color=#FFFF00>(10/30/01 9:32 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub11.ezboard.com/famazonsunitefrm32.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2.topic&index=79>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=C:\WINDOWS\Desktop\Stuff\hypnos.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Apologies</span><hr size=1> *** After talking with Apollo, Hypnos sences all the things that Hera was pondering about and all the trouble that Eris was causing. He walks over to the Queen...*** &quot;Such trouble shes causing, isnt she? Well anyway, if you want me to, who ever is being a bad immortal, I can send them early to bed...&quot; ***Hypnos smirked.*** <p>~*~*~*~*~Thè göd öƒ §|èèp~*~*~*~*~        </p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#6A74B4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/upersepho